        {
          "q": "How can I cancel a subscription?",
          "a": "From the \"Subscriptions\" section, select the subscription and click \"Cancel\". You can pause the subscription if you want to reactivate it later."
        },
        {
          "q": "What should I do if I am not satisfied with the service?",
          "a": "Contact us via WhatsApp or email within 24 hours of service completion. We will review the situation and offer an appropriate solution."
        },
        {
          "q": "How can I change my payment method?",
          "a": "Go to \"Payments\" in the sidebar to add or remove cards. The payment method can also be changed at the time of booking."
